<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<body style="font-family: sans-serif; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; background: #FDF8FC;">
  <div style="background: #FFF0F6; border-radius: 16px; padding: 32px;">
    <h2 style="color: #C2527A; margin-bottom: 8px;">안녕하세요, <%= @user.name %>님 💌</h2>
    <p style="color: #7A4868;">코치가 Day <%= @content.day_number %>의 응답에 피드백을 남겨주셨어요.</p>

    <div style="background: white; border-radius: 12px; padding: 20px; margin: 20px 0; border-left: 4px solid #C2527A;">
      <p style="font-size: 13px; color: #7A4868; margin-bottom: 8px;">📝 내 응답</p>
      <p style="color: #1F0D18;"><%= @response.content %></p>
    </div>

    <div style="background: #FFF0F6; border-radius: 12px; padding: 20px; margin: 20px 0; border-left: 4px solid #8E3A6E;">
      <p style="font-size: 13px; color: #8E3A6E; margin-bottom: 8px;">💬 코치의 피드백</p>
      <p style="color: #1F0D18;"><%= @response.feedback_text %></p>
    </div>

    <a href="<%= my_journey_url %>" style="display: inline-block; background: #C2527A; color: white; padding: 12px 24px; border-radius: 8px; text-decoration: none;">여정 일지에서 확인하기</a>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
